{"type":"data","nodes":[{"type":"data","data":[{"categories":1,"event_categories":27},[2,9,15,21],{"id":3,"attributes":4},1,{"slug":5,"name":6,"description":7,"createdAt":8,"updatedAt":8},"nutrition","營養隨筆",null,"2023-02-12T02:39:02.691Z",{"id":10,"attributes":11},2,{"slug":12,"name":13,"description":7,"createdAt":14,"updatedAt":14},"reflection","感悟隨筆","2023-02-12T02:39:02.692Z",{"id":16,"attributes":17},3,{"slug":18,"name":19,"description":7,"createdAt":20,"updatedAt":20},"fitness","運動筆記","2023-02-12T02:39:02.697Z",{"id":22,"attributes":23},4,{"slug":24,"name":25,"description":7,"createdAt":26,"updatedAt":26},"spiritual","心靈勵志","2023-02-12T02:39:02.698Z",[28,33,38,43,47,52],{"id":3,"attributes":29},{"name":30,"slug":31,"description":7,"createdAt":32,"updatedAt":32},"讀書會","book-sharing","2023-02-12T02:38:55.939Z",{"id":16,"attributes":34},{"name":35,"slug":36,"description":7,"createdAt":37,"updatedAt":37},"文化導賞","cultural","2023-02-12T02:38:55.943Z",{"id":22,"attributes":39},{"name":40,"slug":41,"description":7,"createdAt":42,"updatedAt":42},"遊山玩水","hiking","2023-02-12T02:38:55.946Z",{"id":44,"attributes":45},5,{"name":46,"slug":18,"description":7,"createdAt":42,"updatedAt":42},"健體運動",{"id":48,"attributes":49},6,{"name":50,"slug":5,"description":7,"createdAt":51,"updatedAt":51},"活學營養","2023-02-12T02:38:55.947Z",{"id":10,"attributes":53},{"name":54,"slug":55,"description":7,"createdAt":56,"updatedAt":57},"名人面對面","be-our-guest","2023-02-12T02:38:55.942Z","2023-03-08T13:16:12.875Z"],"uses":{"dependencies":["http://127.0.0.1:1337/api/categories?","http://127.0.0.1:1337/api/event-categories?"]},"slash":"always"},{"type":"data","data":[{"id":1,"attributes":2},241,{"title":3,"excerpt":4,"content":5,"slug":6,"createdAt":7,"updatedAt":8,"author":9,"categories":10,"tags":18,"image":35,"related_posts":74},"心臟充電站",null,"\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(5,5,5);font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif;\"\u003E根據香港衛生防護中心的2014\u002F15人口健康調查，估算10年後即2024\u002F25，每1,000名30-74歲香港人，就有106人可能患上心血管疾病；每10名45-54歲香港人，有近3人被歸類為心血管疾病中風險或高風險人士。\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(5,5,5);font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif;\"\u003E心臟病已成為香港第3位最常見的致命疾病。2020年，因心臟病而死亡的有6,561人，佔總死亡人數約13%，較2019年上升6.5%。\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(5,5,5);font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif;\"\u003E一項追蹤新冠康復者健康狀況的大型研究於2020-21年調查了15.38萬名新冠康復者，發現他們患上不同種類心血管疾病的風險均大增，當中心肌炎激增4.4倍，心臟衰竭上升72%，中風亦飆52%。\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(5,5,5);font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif;\"\u003E自我檢測心血管健康有不同方法，當中歐洲心臟學會的研究指出步行4層樓所需時間若超過1分半鐘，兼伴隨胸口痛、氣促等情況，有可能表示心臟功能出現問題；當然亦要同時考慮其他因素的影響，例如關節健康、貧血和運動能力。\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(5,5,5);font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif;\"\u003E幸好如世界衛生組織所言，大部份心血管疾病皆可預防。在此跟大家分享7大秘訣：\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"color:rgb(5,5,5);font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif;\"\u003E\u003Cimg src=\"https:\u002F\u002Fstatic.xx.fbcdn.net\u002Fimages\u002Femoji.php\u002Fv9\u002Ft5\u002F2\u002F16\u002F1f493.png\" alt=\"💓\"\u003E\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(5,5,5);font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif;\"\u003E不吸煙\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"color:rgb(5,5,5);font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif;\"\u003E\u003Cimg src=\"https:\u002F\u002Fstatic.xx.fbcdn.net\u002Fimages\u002Femoji.php\u002Fv9\u002Ft5\u002F2\u002F16\u002F1f493.png\" alt=\"💓\"\u003E\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(5,5,5);font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif;\"\u003E減喝酒\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"color:rgb(5,5,5);font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif;\"\u003E\u003Cimg src=\"https:\u002F\u002Fstatic.xx.fbcdn.net\u002Fimages\u002Femoji.php\u002Fv9\u002Ft5\u002F2\u002F16\u002F1f493.png\" alt=\"💓\"\u003E\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(5,5,5);font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif;\"\u003E低糖份\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"color:rgb(5,5,5);font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif;\"\u003E\u003Cimg src=\"https:\u002F\u002Fstatic.xx.fbcdn.net\u002Fimages\u002Femoji.php\u002Fv9\u002Ft5\u002F2\u002F16\u002F1f493.png\" alt=\"💓\"\u003E\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(5,5,5);font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif;\"\u003E高纖維\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"color:rgb(5,5,5);font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif;\"\u003E\u003Cimg src=\"https:\u002F\u002Fstatic.xx.fbcdn.net\u002Fimages\u002Femoji.php\u002Fv9\u002Ft5\u002F2\u002F16\u002F1f493.png\" alt=\"💓\"\u003E\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(5,5,5);font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif;\"\u003E多蔬果（紅色蔬果尤其促進心臟健康）\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"color:rgb(5,5,5);font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif;\"\u003E\u003Cimg src=\"https:\u002F\u002Fstatic.xx.fbcdn.net\u002Fimages\u002Femoji.php\u002Fv9\u002Ft5\u002F2\u002F16\u002F1f493.png\" alt=\"💓\"\u003E\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(5,5,5);font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif;\"\u003E睡得足\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"color:rgb(5,5,5);font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif;\"\u003E\u003Cimg src=\"https:\u002F\u002Fstatic.xx.fbcdn.net\u002Fimages\u002Femoji.php\u002Fv9\u002Ft5\u002F2\u002F16\u002F1f493.png\" alt=\"💓\"\u003E\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(5,5,5);font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif;\"\u003E心情好\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(5,5,5);font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif;\"\u003E此外，輔酵素Q10一向被公認為養心補品，主因有二：\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"color:rgb(5,5,5);font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif;\"\u003E\u003Cimg src=\"https:\u002F\u002Fstatic.xx.fbcdn.net\u002Fimages\u002Femoji.php\u002Fv9\u002Ft59\u002F2\u002F16\u002F31_20e3.png\" alt=\"1️⃣\"\u003E\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(5,5,5);font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif;\"\u003E參與“細胞能量貨幣”ATP合成，為肌肉收縮和其他重要的細胞功能提供能量\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"color:rgb(5,5,5);font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif;\"\u003E\u003Cimg src=\"https:\u002F\u002Fstatic.xx.fbcdn.net\u002Fimages\u002Femoji.php\u002Fv9\u002Ft78\u002F2\u002F16\u002F32_20e3.png\" alt=\"2️⃣\"\u003E\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(5,5,5);font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif;\"\u003E重要的脂質抗氧化劑，防止血管出現氧化傷害\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(5,5,5);font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif;\"\u003E米契爾博士 Dr Peter Mitchell 正正因為發現細胞製造能量必需輔酵素Q10的參與，輔酵素Q10的含量是保證人體生命活力的關鍵，而榮獲第78屆諾貝爾奬。\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(5,5,5);font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif;\"\u003E40歲後，人體合成輔酵素Q10的能力大跌，心臟和腎臟的輔酵素Q10含量平均只有68.2%及72.6%。因此，建議40歲後每天補充至少30毫克輔酵素Q10，相當於進食300隻雞蛋\u002F100個橙\u002F35安士牛肉。\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(5,5,5);font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif;\"\u003E由於單從食物實在難以攝取充夠份量的輔酵素Q10，建議大家可選擇天然有機的補充品，如能配合左旋肉鹼及氨基乙磺酸，與輔酵素Q10相輔相成，將進一步促進心臟健康，強化器官。\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E&nbsp;\u003C\u002Fp\u003E","heartcharger","2023-08-06T01:39:03.496Z","2023-08-06T06:46:38.364Z",{"data":4},{"data":11},[12],{"id":13,"attributes":14},1,{"slug":15,"name":16,"description":4,"createdAt":17,"updatedAt":17},"nutrition","營養隨筆","2023-02-12T02:39:02.691Z",{"data":19},[20,25,30],{"id":21,"attributes":22},209,{"name":23,"createdAt":24,"updatedAt":24},"心臟健康","2023-02-12T03:32:01.389Z",{"id":26,"attributes":27},242,{"name":28,"createdAt":29,"updatedAt":29},"心血管健康","2023-02-12T03:32:01.403Z",{"id":31,"attributes":32},224,{"name":33,"createdAt":34,"updatedAt":34},"輔酵素Q10","2023-02-12T03:32:01.396Z",{"data":36},{"id":37,"attributes":38},7,{"name":39,"alternativeText":4,"caption":4,"width":40,"height":40,"formats":41,"hash":68,"ext":43,"mime":46,"size":69,"url":70,"previewUrl":4,"provider":71,"provider_metadata":4,"createdAt":72,"updatedAt":73},"315550763_5893382900681931_7918747814927541091_n.jpg",1080,{"large":42,"small":50,"medium":56,"thumbnail":62},{"ext":43,"url":44,"hash":45,"mime":46,"name":47,"path":4,"size":48,"width":49,"height":49},".jpg","https:\u002F\u002Fempowerhk.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com\u002Flarge_315550763_5893382900681931_7918747814927541091_n_50b47677db.jpg","large_315550763_5893382900681931_7918747814927541091_n_50b47677db","image\u002Fjpeg","large_315550763_5893382900681931_7918747814927541091_n.jpg",61.43,1000,{"ext":43,"url":51,"hash":52,"mime":46,"name":53,"path":4,"size":54,"width":55,"height":55},"https:\u002F\u002Fempowerhk.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com\u002Fsmall_315550763_5893382900681931_7918747814927541091_n_50b47677db.jpg","small_315550763_5893382900681931_7918747814927541091_n_50b47677db","small_315550763_5893382900681931_7918747814927541091_n.jpg",25.78,500,{"ext":43,"url":57,"hash":58,"mime":46,"name":59,"path":4,"size":60,"width":61,"height":61},"https:\u002F\u002Fempowerhk.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com\u002Fmedium_315550763_5893382900681931_7918747814927541091_n_50b47677db.jpg","medium_315550763_5893382900681931_7918747814927541091_n_50b47677db","medium_315550763_5893382900681931_7918747814927541091_n.jpg",42.36,750,{"ext":43,"url":63,"hash":64,"mime":46,"name":65,"path":4,"size":66,"width":67,"height":67},"https:\u002F\u002Fempowerhk.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com\u002Fthumbnail_315550763_5893382900681931_7918747814927541091_n_50b47677db.jpg","thumbnail_315550763_5893382900681931_7918747814927541091_n_50b47677db","thumbnail_315550763_5893382900681931_7918747814927541091_n.jpg",5.73,156,"315550763_5893382900681931_7918747814927541091_n_50b47677db",57.11,"https:\u002F\u002Fempowerhk.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com\u002F315550763_5893382900681931_7918747814927541091_n_50b47677db.jpg","aws-s3","2023-08-06T01:34:30.365Z","2023-08-06T01:38:01.838Z",{"data":75},[76],{"id":21,"attributes":77},{"title":78,"excerpt":4,"content":79,"slug":80,"createdAt":81,"updatedAt":81},"做個“好心”人","\n\n根據香港衞生署衞生防護中心，心臟病是香港疾病第3大殺手，僅次於腫瘤癌症和肺炎😖。心臟是人體的核心供能“設備”，心肌、脈管、瓣膜就像其中的精密零件，一旦某個部位損壞，心臟功能就會部份失靈，甚至威脅全身健康🥺。\n那麼身體會如何發出預警訊號，保護心臟這人體發動機呢？💪🏻\n\n1️⃣頸項變粗\u003Cbr\u003E\n美國曾對3,000多名研究對象，發現脖子越粗的人，心血管疾病風險就越大😳。一般情況下，若男性頸圍超過39厘米，女性頸圍超過35厘米，就是脖子較粗。\n\n2️⃣臉部浮腫\u003Cbr\u003E\n若臉形出現腫脹，臉部肌肉組織鬆弛，用手指壓會出現壓痕，或壓痕部位的皮膚彈不起來，可能預示心臟出現問題，應馬上處理。\n\n3️⃣嘴唇發紫\u003Cbr\u003E\n嘴唇發青發紫或唇邊呈現青紫色，可能存在血液循環不良導致的心臟問題；若滿臉通紅，則很可能是二尖瓣狹窄所致。\n\n4️⃣瞼黃斑瘤\u003Cbr\u003E\n對於中老年人來說，眼部周圍出現黃色小腫塊（一般為米粒或黃豆大小），可能反映體內脂質代謝存在障礙，也是誘發心臟病的重要因素。\n\n5️⃣下巴疼痛\u003Cbr\u003E\n典型的心絞痛始於胸骨後方，患者會感到胸部有壓力，甚至有燒灼、擠壓和緊繃感；同時，臂部、脖頸、肩膀、上腹部、後背或下巴也會感到疼痛或不適。\n\n6️⃣耳垂皺摺\u003Cbr\u003E\n耳垂有許多微血管，當血管硬化或收窄，造成血液供血不足，就容易在耳珠上方1\u002F3處形成內側往外側下垂的刻痕，名為“法蘭克徵兆”（Frank’s sign）。\n\n7️⃣呼吸不暢\u003Cbr\u003E\n爬一段樓梯就氣喘，而過去從來沒有這種現象，應警惕心臟問題。躺下時出現呼吸問題，很可能是心臟瓣膜病的癥狀。\n\n8️⃣大量冒汗\u003Cbr\u003E\n突然間大汗淋漓而沒有明確原因，要高度懷疑是否心臟出了問題。心輸出量的大量減少和交感神經的過度活躍，會造成心臟病發作的出汗癥狀。\n\n💪🏻戒掉壞習慣 做個“好心”人\u003Cbr\u003E\n1️⃣戒煙限酒\u003Cbr\u003E\n吸煙對心臟的損害長期且頑固，煙草中的尼古丁可刺激心臟傳導系統，使心跳加快，增加心臟負荷。研究顯示停止吸煙20分鐘，因吸煙而飆升的血壓和心率即可平緩下來。\n飲酒使血管處於擴張和血流加速狀態，心率加快，容易導致心臟病急性發作。\n\n2️⃣少鹽低鈉\u003Cbr\u003E\n鹽份攝取與高血壓息息相關。高血壓導致心臟的負荷加重，增加患上冠心病、高血壓性心臟病及中風的風險。\n\n3️⃣降低血脂\u003Cbr\u003E\n血脂過高會導致脂肪在血管中堆積，容易引致冠心病。要有效降低血脂，可以增加以下營養素的攝入：\u003Cbr\u003E\n🌟鎂：有助降低壞膽固醇，促進血管擴張，改善心肌缺血\u003Cbr\u003E\n🌟優質脂肪酸：包括OMEGA-3及橄欖油\u003Cbr\u003E\n🌟膳食纖維\u003Cbr\u003E\n🌟西醫在心血管疾病的臨床防治的處方中，往往都包含輔酵素Q10，是西方應用最廣泛的心臟保養劑，臨床試驗功效顯著：\u003Cbr\u003E\n❤️心律不正：67%心電圖回復正常，頭昏胸悶獲得改善\u003Cbr\u003E\n❤️心絞痛：發作次數減少，氣短心悸得到改善\u003Cbr\u003E\n❤️心臟衰竭：2\u002F3患者心臟功能明顯改善\n\n4️⃣控制體重\u003Cbr\u003E\n肥胖容易引起內分泌激素分泌異常，導致內臟脂肪更易分解，血脂升高；加上體內各種代謝紊亂，形成惡性循環，影響心臟功能。\n\n健康減重，減肥而不減肌，促進新陳代謝，對做個“好心”人大有幫助🥰。","heart-nutrition210605","2021-06-05T00:00:00.000Z"],"uses":{"dependencies":["http://127.0.0.1:1337/api/posts?populate[author]=true&populate[categories]=true&populate[tags]=true&populate[image]=true&populate[related_posts]=true&filters[slug][$eq]=heartcharger"],"params":["slug"]}}]}